==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: A book holds a face as smooth as jade.
===Proverb===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' shū zhōng zì yŏu yán rú yù, shu1zhong1zi4you3yan2ru2yu4)
# If you study hard, you will be successful, and a beautiful woman will want to marry you.

